data.name: lblRules.Text
data.value: ----------------------------------------------------- Don't let the Aliens touch the ground! ----------------------------------------------------- Defend your territory by moving around with A and D, and shoooting with Space ----------------------------------------------------- Aliens: Grounder -- Speedy, and goes for the ground fast. Best to shoot it down quick. Waver-- Travels horizontally until it comes across an obstacle, to which it moves down and changes direction. The more aliens there are for this guy to bump into, the more threataning it is. Avoider-- Master dodger. If it sees a laser in front of it, it'll move out of the way. You must catch it off-guard. -----------------------------------------------------
